title: MisterMusic Show 349-indie,alternative rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 349 - 120 min. [192 kbps stereo]-



New music on the show this week by Someone Still Loves You Boris Yeltsin, Death Cab For Cutie, and Circa Waves.
The 'Oldie of the Week' is a modern rock hit, that remained number 1 on the chart for 4 weeks during April 1995. 
A song that wasn't intended to be a single from the album-but topped the charts, 20 years ago.

Plus a mix of over 5 decades of classic indie, alternative and rock hits.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
